[
  {
    "id": "kp-4.1-01",
    "section": "4.1",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Angle Properties of Lines and Triangles",
    "title_zh": "线与三角形的角度性质",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Angles are measured in degrees and follow specific rules based on their position.\n\n**Angles on a straight line** always sum to $180^\\circ$. **Angles at a point** sum to $360^\\circ$. **Vertically opposite angles** are equal.\n\n**Parallel lines** create specific angle pairs when cut by a transversal: **Alternate angles** are equal (Z-shape), **Corresponding angles** are equal (F-shape), and **Co-interior angles** sum to $180^\\circ$ (C-shape).\n\n**Triangles** have an interior angle sum of $180^\\circ$. An **exterior angle** of a triangle is equal to the sum of the two opposite interior angles.",
      "zh": "角度以度为单位，并根据其位置遵循特定的规则。\n\n**直在线的角度**之和总是 $180^\\circ$。**点周围的角度**之和为 $360^\\circ$。**对顶角**相等。\n\n**平行线**被截线相交时产生特定的角对：**内错角**相等（Z形），**同位角**相等（F形），**同旁内角**之和为 $180^\\circ$（C形）。\n\n**三角形**的内角和为 $180^\\circ$。三角形的**外角**等于两个不相邻内角之和。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-parallel-angles",
        "label": "Calculate angles in parallel lines",
        "label_zh": "计算平行线中的角度",
        "description": "Find missing angles using alternate, corresponding, or co-interior angle properties, often requiring multiple steps.",
        "description_zh": "利用内错角、同位角或同旁内角的性质求缺失的角度，通常需要多个步骤。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-parallel-angles",
        "question": "Two parallel lines are crossed by a transversal. One angle is $75^\\circ$. Find the size of its co-interior angle.",
        "question_zh": "两条平行线被一条截线相交。其中一个角是 $75^\\circ$。求其同旁内角的大小。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Recall the property of co-interior angles.\nCo-interior angles sum to $180^\\circ$.\n\n**Step 2:** Subtract the given angle from $180^\\circ$.\n$180^\\circ - 75^\\circ = 105^\\circ$.\n\n**Answer:** $105^\\circ$.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 回忆同旁内角的性质。\n同旁内角之和为 $180^\\circ$。\n\n**步骤2：** 从 $180^\\circ$ 中减去已知角。\n$180^\\circ - 75^\\circ = 105^\\circ$。\n\n**答案：** $105^\\circ$。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/1F/May/2019"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-parallel-angles",
        "question": "In triangle $ABC$, angle $A = 40^\\circ$ and angle $B = 85^\\circ$. Find the exterior angle at $C$.",
        "question_zh": "在三角形 $ABC$ 中，角 $A = 40^\\circ$，角 $B = 85^\\circ$。求 $C$ 点处的外角。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Use the exterior angle theorem.\nExterior angle = Sum of opposite interior angles.\n\n**Step 2:** Calculate the sum.\n$40^\\circ + 85^\\circ = 125^\\circ$.\n\n**Answer:** $125^\\circ$.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 使用三角形外角定理。\n外角 = 不相邻内角之和。\n\n**步骤2：** 计算总和。\n$40^\\circ + 85^\\circ = 125^\\circ$。\n\n**答案：** $125^\\circ$。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "What is the sum of angles in a triangle?",
        "q_zh": "三角形的内角和是多少？",
        "o": [
          "$90^\\circ$",
          "$180^\\circ$",
          "$270^\\circ$",
          "$360^\\circ$"
        ],
        "a": 1,
        "e": "The angles in any triangle always add up to $180^\\circ$.",
        "e_zh": "任何三角形的内角和总是 $180^\\circ$。"
      },
      {
        "q": "Which type of angles are equal and form a 'Z' shape on parallel lines?",
        "q_zh": "在平行线上，哪种类型的角相等并形成“Z”字形？",
        "o": [
          "Corresponding angles",
          "Co-interior angles",
          "Alternate angles",
          "Vertically opposite angles"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "Alternate angles are equal and can be identified by a Z-shape formed by the parallel lines and the transversal.",
        "e_zh": "内错角相等，可以通过平行线和截线形成的 Z 字形来识别。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [],
    "tier": "both"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-4.2-01",
    "section": "4.2",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Angles in Polygons",
    "title_zh": "多边形中的角度",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Polygons follow general formulas for their interior and exterior angles.\n\n**Sum of interior angles** for an $n$-sided polygon is $(n-2) \\times 180^\\circ$. For a **regular polygon**, each interior angle is $\\frac{(n-2) \\times 180^\\circ}{n}$.\n\n**Sum of exterior angles** for any polygon is always $360^\\circ$. For a regular polygon, each exterior angle is $\\frac{360^\\circ}{n}$.\n\n**Interior and exterior angles** at any vertex of a polygon always sum to $180^\\circ$ as they lie on a straight line.",
      "zh": "多边形的内角和外角遵循通用的公式。\n\n**n 边形的内角和**为 $(n-2) \\times 180^\\circ$。对于**正多边形**，每个内角为 $\\frac{(n-2) \\times 180^\\circ}{n}$。\n\n任何多边形的**外角和**总是 $360^\\circ$。对于正多边形，每个外角为 $\\frac{360^\\circ}{n}$。\n\n在多边形的任何顶点处，**内角与外角**之和总是 $180^\\circ$，因为它们位于一条直线上。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-polygon-sides",
        "label": "Find the number of sides of a regular polygon",
        "label_zh": "求正多边形的边数",
        "description": "Given an interior or exterior angle, calculate $n$ using the formulas.",
        "description_zh": "已知一个内角或外角，利用公式计算边数 $n$。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-polygon-sides",
        "question": "A regular polygon has an exterior angle of $40^\\circ$. Calculate the number of sides it has.",
        "question_zh": "一个正多边形的一个外角是 $40^\\circ$。计算它的边数。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Use the exterior angle formula: Exterior angle $= \\frac{360^\\circ}{n}$.\n\n**Step 2:** Substitute the given value and solve for $n$.\n$40^\\circ = \\frac{360^\\circ}{n}$\n$n = \\frac{360}{40} = 9$.\n\n**Answer:** $9$ sides.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 使用外角公式：外角 $= \\frac{360^\\circ}{n}$。\n\n**步骤2：** 代入已知值并解 $n$。\n$40^\\circ = \\frac{360^\\circ}{n}$\n$n = \\frac{360}{40} = 9$。\n\n**答案：** $9$ 条边。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/2H/Jan/2020"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-polygon-sum",
        "question": "Calculate the sum of the interior angles of a hexagon.",
        "question_zh": "计算六边形的内角和。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Identify the number of sides. A hexagon has $n=6$.\n\n**Step 2:** Apply the formula $(n-2) \\times 180^\\circ$.\n$(6-2) \\times 180^\\circ = 4 \\times 180^\\circ = 720^\\circ$.\n\n**Answer:** $720^\\circ$.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 确定边数。六边形有 $n=6$。\n\n**步骤2：** 应用公式 $(n-2) \\times 180^\\circ$。\n$(6-2) \\times 180^\\circ = 4 \\times 180^\\circ = 720^\\circ$。\n\n**答案：** $720^\\circ$。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "What is the exterior angle of a regular octagon?",
        "q_zh": "正八边形的一个外角是多少？",
        "o": [
          "$45^\\circ$",
          "$60^\\circ$",
          "$135^\\circ$",
          "$360^\\circ$"
        ],
        "a": 0,
        "e": "For an octagon, $n=8$. Exterior angle $= 360 / 8 = 45^\\circ$.",
        "e_zh": "对于八边形，$n=8$。外角 $= 360 / 8 = 45^\\circ$。"
      },
      {
        "q": "If the sum of interior angles is $1080^\\circ$, how many sides does the polygon have?",
        "q_zh": "如果内角和是 $1080^\\circ$，这个多边形有多少条边？",
        "o": [
          "6",
          "7",
          "8",
          "10"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "$(n-2) \\times 180 = 1080 \\Rightarrow n-2 = 6 \\Rightarrow n = 8$.",
        "e_zh": "$(n-2) \\times 180 = 1080 \\Rightarrow n-2 = 6 \\Rightarrow n = 8$。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [],
    "tier": "both"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-4.3-01",
    "section": "4.3",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Symmetry",
    "title_zh": "对称",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Symmetry describes how a shape can be transformed while looking the same.\n\n**Line symmetry** (Reflectional symmetry) occurs if a shape can be folded along a line so that the two halves match exactly. The fold line is called the **line of symmetry**.\n\n**Rotational symmetry** occurs if a shape looks exactly the same after being rotated by an angle less than $360^\\circ$ about its center. The **order of rotational symmetry** is the number of times the shape looks the same during a full $360^\\circ$ turn.",
      "zh": "对称描述了一个图形在变换后保持外观不变的性质。\n\n**轴对称**（反射对称）：如果一个图形可以沿一条直线折叠，使两半完全重合，则称其具有轴对称。折痕被称为**对称轴**。\n\n**旋转对称**：如果一个图形绕其中心旋转小于 $360^\\circ$ 的角度后外观完全相同，则称其具有旋转对称。**旋转对称的阶数**是指在旋转 $360^\\circ$ 的过程中，图形看起来相同的次数。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-symmetry-properties",
        "label": "Identify symmetry in 2D shapes",
        "label_zh": "识别 2D 图形的对称性",
        "description": "State the number of lines of symmetry and the order of rotational symmetry for a given shape.",
        "description_zh": "说明给定图形的对称轴数量和旋转对称阶数。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-symmetry-properties",
        "question": "A square is drawn. Write down:\n(a) the number of lines of symmetry\n(b) the order of rotational symmetry",
        "question_zh": "画出一个正方形。写出：\n(a) 对称轴的数量\n(b) 旋转对称的阶数",
        "solution": "(a) A square has 4 lines of symmetry (2 through midpoints of sides, 2 diagonals).\n(b) A square has rotational symmetry of order 4 (looks the same every $90^\\circ$ turn).\n\n**Answers:** (a) $4$ (b) $4$",
        "solution_zh": "(a) 正方形有 4 条对称轴（2 条通过对边中点，2 条是对角线）。\n(b) 正方形的旋转对称阶数为 4（每旋转 $90^\\circ$ 外观相同一次）。\n\n**答案：** (a) $4$ (b) $4$",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-symmetry-properties",
        "question": "State the order of rotational symmetry of a regular pentagon.",
        "question_zh": "说明正五边形的旋转对称阶数。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** For any regular $n$-gon, the order of rotational symmetry is $n$.\n\n**Step 2:** A pentagon has $n=5$.\n\n**Answer:** $5$.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 对于任何正 $n$ 边形，旋转对称的阶数就是 $n$。\n\n**步骤2：** 五边形 $n=5$。\n\n**答案：** $5$。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "How many lines of symmetry does an isosceles triangle have?",
        "q_zh": "等腰三角形有多少条对称轴？",
        "o": [
          "0",
          "1",
          "2",
          "3"
        ],
        "a": 1,
        "e": "An isosceles triangle has 1 line of symmetry (through the vertex between equal sides).",
        "e_zh": "等腰三角形有 1 条对称轴（通过两条等边之间的顶点）。"
      },
      {
        "q": "What is the order of rotational symmetry of a parallelogram?",
        "q_zh": "平行四边形的旋转对称阶数是多少？",
        "o": [
          "1",
          "2",
          "3",
          "4"
        ],
        "a": 1,
        "e": "A parallelogram looks the same at $0^\\circ$ and $180^\\circ$, so the order is 2.",
        "e_zh": "平行四边形在 $0^\\circ$ 和 $180^\\circ$ 时看起来相同，所以阶数为 2。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [],
    "tier": "both"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-4.4-01",
    "section": "4.4",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Measures and Bearings",
    "title_zh": "测量与方位角",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Measures involve units of length, mass, and capacity, as well as the concept of bearings.\n\n**Bearings** are angles measured from North ($000^\\circ$) in a **clockwise** direction. They must always be written as **three digits** (e.g., $045^\\circ$ instead of $45^\\circ$).\n\n**Back bearings** (bearing of $A$ from $B$ given the bearing of $B$ from $A$) can be found by adding or subtracting $180^\\circ$.",
      "zh": "测量涉及长度、质量和容量的单位，以及方位角的概念。\n\n**方位角**是从正北方向（$000^\\circ$）开始**顺时针**测量的角度。它们必须始终写成**三位数字**（例如 $045^\\circ$ 而非 $45^\\circ$）。\n\n**反向方位角**（已知 $A$ 到 $B$ 的方位角，求 $B$ 到 $A$ 的方位角）可以通过加上或减去 $180^\\circ$ 来求得。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-bearing-calc",
        "label": "Calculate bearings using geometry",
        "label_zh": "利用几何知识计算方位角",
        "description": "Find bearings between points using parallel line properties (alternate/co-interior angles).",
        "description_zh": "利用平行线性质（内错角/同旁内角）求两点间的方位角。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-bearing-calc",
        "question": "The bearing of ship $B$ from ship $A$ is $120^\\circ$. Find the bearing of ship $A$ from ship $B$.",
        "question_zh": "船 $B$ 在船 $A$ 的 $120^\\circ$ 方向。求船 $A$ 在船 $B$ 的方位角。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Draw North lines at $A$ and $B$. These are parallel.\n\n**Step 2:** Use co-interior angles. The interior angle between the North line at $B$ and the line $AB$ is $180^\\circ - 120^\\circ = 60^\\circ$.\n\n**Step 3:** The bearing is measured clockwise from North. Bearing $= 360^\\circ - 60^\\circ = 300^\\circ$. (Alternatively: $120^\\circ + 180^\\circ = 300^\\circ$ since $120 < 180$).\n\n**Answer:** $300^\\circ$.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 在 $A$ 和 $B$ 点画出北线。它们是平行的。\n\n**步骤2：** 使用同旁内角。$B$ 点北线与直线 $AB$ 之间的内角为 $180^\\circ - 120^\\circ = 60^\\circ$。\n\n**步骤3：** 方位角是顺时针测量的。方位角 $= 360^\\circ - 60^\\circ = 300^\\circ$。（或者：由于 $120 < 180$，直接用 $120^\\circ + 180^\\circ = 300^\\circ$）。\n\n**答案：** $300^\\circ$。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/1H/Jan/2021"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-unit-conv",
        "question": "Convert $5.4$ km to meters.",
        "question_zh": "将 $5.4$ 千米转换为米。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Know that $1$ km $= 1000$ m.\n\n**Step 2:** Multiply by $1000$.\n$5.4 \\times 1000 = 5400$.\n\n**Answer:** $5400$ m.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 已知 $1$ km $= 1000$ m。\n\n**步骤2：** 乘以 $1000$。\n$5.4 \\times 1000 = 5400$。\n\n**答案：** $5400$ m。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "What is the bearing of South-West?",
        "q_zh": "西南方向的方位角是多少？",
        "o": [
          "$045^\\circ$",
          "$135^\\circ$",
          "$225^\\circ$",
          "$315^\\circ$"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "South is $180^\\circ$ and West is $270^\\circ$. South-West is exactly halfway: $225^\\circ$.",
        "e_zh": "正南是 $180^\\circ$，正西是 $270^\\circ$。西南正处于中间：$225^\\circ$。"
      },
      {
        "q": "If the bearing of $X$ from $Y$ is $070^\\circ$, what is the bearing of $Y$ from $X$?",
        "q_zh": "如果 $Y$ 到 $X$ 的方位角是 $070^\\circ$，那么 $X$ 到 $Y$ 的方位角是多少？",
        "o": [
          "$110^\\circ$",
          "$250^\\circ$",
          "$290^\\circ$",
          "$070^\\circ$"
        ],
        "a": 1,
        "e": "Add $180^\\circ$ to the bearing: $70^\\circ + 180^\\circ = 250^\\circ$.",
        "e_zh": "在方位角上加上 $180^\\circ$：$70^\\circ + 180^\\circ = 250^\\circ$。"
      }
    ],
    "vocabLinks": [],
    "tier": "both"
  },
  {
    "id": "kp-4.5-01",
    "section": "4.5",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Constructions and Loci",
    "title_zh": "作图与轨迹",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Construction involves drawing accurate diagrams using only a ruler and compasses. **Construction arcs** must always be visible.\n\n**Perpendicular bisector** is the set of points equidistant from two fixed points. **Angle bisector** is the set of points equidistant from two intersecting lines.\n\n**Loci** (plural of locus) refer to the set of points that satisfy a particular rule. For example, a locus of points at a fixed distance from a point is a circle. A locus of points at a fixed distance from a line consists of two parallel lines with semi-circles at the ends.",
      "zh": "作图涉及仅使用直尺和圆规绘制精确的图表。**作图弧线**必须始终保持可见。\n\n**垂直平分线**是到两个定点距离相等的点的集合。**角平分线**是到两条相交直线距离相等的点的集合。\n\n**轨迹**（locus 的复数）是指满足特定规则的点的集合。例如，到定点距离固定的点的轨迹是一个圆。到直线距离固定的点的轨迹由两条平行线和两端的半圆组成。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-locus-region",
        "label": "Shade a region based on loci",
        "label_zh": "根据轨迹阴影化区域",
        "description": "Construct multiple loci (e.g., bisectors) and shade the region that satisfies conditions like 'closer to A than B'.",
        "description_zh": "构造多个轨迹（如平分线）并为满足“离 A 比离 B 近”等条件的区域涂色。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-locus-region",
        "question": "Points $A$ and $B$ are $8$ cm apart. Construct the locus of points that are exactly $5$ cm from $A$.",
        "question_zh": "$A$ 点和 $B$ 点相距 $8$ 厘米。作图求到 $A$ 点距离恰好为 $5$ 厘米的点的轨迹。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Use a ruler to set your compasses to a width of $5$ cm.\n\n**Step 2:** Place the compass needle on point $A$.\n\n**Step 3:** Draw a full circle (or arc) around $A$.\n\n**Answer:** A circle of radius $5$ cm with center $A$.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 使用直尺将圆规半径设置为 $5$ 厘米。\n\n**步骤2：** 将圆规尖端置于 $A$ 点。\n\n**步骤3：** 围绕 $A$ 画一个完整的圆（或圆弧）。\n\n**答案：** 以 $A$ 为圆心，半径为 $5$ 厘米的圆。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-bisector",
        "question": "On a map, shade the region that is less than $3$ km from point $C$ and closer to line $AB$ than line $AD$.",
        "question_zh": "在地图上，对距离 $C$ 点小于 $3$ 公里且距离直线 $AB$ 比距离直线 $AD$ 近的区域进行阴影处理。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Construct a circle around $C$ with radius representing $3$ km (using scale).\n\n**Step 2:** Construct the angle bisector of angle $BAD$ to find points equidistant from $AB$ and $AD$.\n\n**Step 3:** Shade the area inside the circle and on the $AB$ side of the bisector.\n\n**Result:** Region satisfies both boundaries.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 以 $C$ 为圆心，以代表 $3$ 公里的半径画圆（使用比例尺）。\n\n**步骤2：** 作角 $BAD$ 的角平分线，找到到 $AB$ 和 $AD$ 距离相等的点。\n\n**步骤3：** 在圆内且在角平分线靠近 $AB$ 一侧的区域涂上阴影。\n\n**结果：** 满足两个边界条件的区域。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/2H/May/2018"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "The perpendicular bisector of a line segment $AB$ is the locus of all points that are...",
        "q_zh": "线段 $AB$ 的垂直平分线是所有满足以下条件的点的轨迹...",
        "o": [
          "Fixed distance from A",
          "Equidistant from A and B",
          "Equidistant from line AB",
          "On the line AB"
        ],
        "a": 1,
        "e": "The perpendicular bisector consists of all points that are the same distance from $A$ as they are from $B$.",
