    "id": "kp-4.6-01",
    "section": "4.6",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Circle Theorems",
    "title_zh": "圆的几何定理",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Circle theorems are rules describing the relationships between angles, lines, and circles.\n\n**Angle at the centre** is twice the angle at the circumference standing on the same arc. **Angle in a semi-circle** is always $90^\\circ$.\n\n**Angles in the same segment** are equal. **Cyclic quadrilaterals** have opposite angles that sum to $180^\\circ$.\n\n**Alternate segment theorem** states that the angle between a tangent and a chord is equal to the angle in the alternate segment.",
      "zh": "圆的定理是描述角、线和圆之间关系的规则。\n\n**圆心角**是同一段弧所对圆周角的两倍。**半圆上的圆周角**总是 $90^\\circ$。\n\n**同弧所对的圆周角**相等。**圆内接四边形**的对角之和为 $180^\\circ$。\n\n**弦切角定理**（交错弓形定理）指出：切线与弦之间的夹角等于该弦所对的内错弓形角。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
