        "patternId": "ep-circle-proof",
        "question": "Points $A, B, C$ are on a circle with center $O$. Angle $ABC = 40^\\circ$. Find angle $AOC$.",
        "question_zh": "$A, B, C$ 点在以 $O$ 为圆心的圆上。角 $ABC = 40^\\circ$。求角 $AOC$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Identify the relevant theorem.\nThe angle at the center is twice the angle at the circumference.\n\n**Step 2:** Calculate the angle.\nAngle $AOC = 2 \\times 40^\\circ = 80^\\circ$.\n\n**Answer:** $80^\\circ$ (Reason: Angle at center is twice angle at circumference).",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 识别相关定理。\n圆心角是圆周角的两倍。\n\n**步骤2：** 计算角度。\n角 $AOC = 2 \\times 40^\\circ = 80^\\circ$。\n\n**答案：** $80^\\circ$（理由：同弧所对圆心角是圆周角的两倍）。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/1H/May/2022"
