        "patternId": "ep-circle-proof",
        "question": "$ABCD$ is a cyclic quadrilateral. Angle $A = 110^\\circ$. Find angle $C$.",
        "question_zh": "$ABCD$ 是圆内接四边形。角 $A = 110^\\circ$。求角 $C$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Recall the cyclic quadrilateral property.\nOpposite angles sum to $180^\\circ$.\n\n**Step 2:** Calculate.\nAngle $C = 180^\\circ - 110^\\circ = 70^\\circ$.\n\n**Answer:** $70^\\circ$.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 回忆圆内接四边形的性质。\n对角之和为 $180^\\circ$。\n\n**步骤2：** 计算。\n角 $C = 180^\\circ - 110^\\circ = 70^\\circ$。\n\n**答案：** $70^\\circ$。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1"
      }
