    "id": "kp-4.7-01",
    "section": "4.7",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Geometrical Reasoning and Proof",
    "title_zh": "几何推理与证明",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Geometrical reasoning involves using known properties to deduce new information or prove statements.\n\n**Congruent triangles** are identical in shape and size. The four criteria for congruence are: **SSS** (Side-Side-Side), **SAS** (Side-Angle-Side), **ASA** (Angle-Side-Angle), and **RHS** (Right-angle, Hypotenuse, Side).\n\n**Similar triangles** have the same shape but different sizes. Their corresponding angles are equal, and their corresponding sides are in the same ratio.",
      "zh": "几何推理涉及利用已知性质来推导新信息或证明命题。\n\n**全等三角形**在形状和大小上完全相同。全等的四个判定标准是：**SSS**（边边边）、**SAS**（边角边）、**ASA**（角边角）和 **RHS**（直角、斜边、边）。\n\n**相似三角形**形状相同但大小不同。它们的对应角相等，对应边成比例。"
    },
