        "solution": "**Step 1:** Compare the given parts. We have two sides and the included angle.\n\n**Step 2:** Match with a congruence criterion.\nSAS (Side-Angle-Side).\n\n**Answer:** They are congruent by SAS.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 比较已知部分。我们有两条边和它们的夹角。\n\n**步骤2：** 匹配全等判定标准。\nSAS（边角边）。\n\n**答案：** 根据 SAS，它们全等。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1"
