        "question_zh": "三角形 $ABC$ 相似于三角形 $PQR$。$AB = 4$ 厘米，$PQ = 12$ 厘米。如果 $BC = 5$ 厘米，求 $QR$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Find the scale factor.\nScale Factor $= \\frac{PQ}{AB} = \\frac{12}{4} = 3$.\n\n**Step 2:** Multiply the corresponding side by the scale factor.\n$QR = BC \\times 3 = 5 \\times 3 = 15$.\n\n**Answer:** $15$ cm.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 求比例因子。\n比例因子 $= \\frac{PQ}{AB} = \\frac{12}{4} = 3$。\n\n**步骤2：** 将对应边乘以比例因子。\n$QR = BC \\times 3 = 5 \\times 3 = 15$。\n\n**答案：** $15$ 厘米。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/2F/Jan/2021"
