  {
    "id": "kp-4.8-01",
    "section": "4.8",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Pythagoras and Right-Angled Trig",
    "title_zh": "勾股定理与直角三角函数",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "For right-angled triangles, we use Pythagoras' theorem and Trigonometric ratios (SOH CAH TOA).\n\n**Pythagoras' Theorem** states that $a^2 + b^2 = c^2$, where $c$ is the hypotenuse (the longest side opposite the right angle).\n\n**Trigonometric ratios** relate angles and sides:\n$\\sin(\\theta) = \\frac{\\text{Opposite}}{\\text{Hypotenuse}}$\n$\\cos(\\theta) = \\frac{\\text{Adjacent}}{\\text{Hypotenuse}}$\n$\\tan(\\theta) = \\frac{\\text{Opposite}}{\\text{Adjacent}}$",
      "zh": "对于直角三角形，我们使用勾股定理和三角函数比（SOH CAH TOA）。\n\n**勾股定理**指出 $a^2 + b^2 = c^2$，其中 $c$ 是斜边（直角所对的最长边）。\n\n**三角函数比**将角度与边长联系起来：\n$\\sin(\\theta) = \\frac{\\text{对边}}{\\text{斜边}}$\n$\\cos(\\theta) = \\frac{\\text{邻边}}{\\text{斜边}}$\n$\\tan(\\theta) = \\frac{\\text{对边}}{\\text{邻边}}$"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-pythag-calc",
        "label": "Calculate a missing side in a right-angled triangle",
        "label_zh": "计算直角三角形中缺失的边",
        "description": "Use Pythagoras to find the hypotenuse or a shorter side.",
        "description_zh": "利用勾股定理求斜边或直角边。"
      },
      {
        "id": "ep-trig-angle",
        "label": "Find a missing angle using SOHCAHTOA",
        "label_zh": "利用 SOHCAHTOA 求缺失的角度",
        "description": "Use inverse trig functions (e.g., $\\sin^{-1}$) to calculate an angle.",
        "description_zh": "使用反三角函数（如 $\\sin^{-1}$）计算角度。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-pythag-calc",
        "question": "A right-angled triangle has sides of $5$ cm and $12$ cm. Calculate the length of the hypotenuse.",
        "question_zh": "一个直角三角形的直角边分别为 $5$ 厘米和 $12$ 厘米。计算斜边的长度。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Use $a^2 + b^2 = c^2$.\n$5^2 + 12^2 = c^2$\n\n**Step 2:** Calculate squares and sum.\n$25 + 144 = 169$\n\n**Step 3:** Take the square root.\n$c = \\sqrt{169} = 13$.\n\n**Answer:** $13$ cm.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 使用 $a^2 + b^2 = c^2$。\n$5^2 + 12^2 = c^2$\n\n**步骤2：** 计算平方和。\n$25 + 144 = 169$\n\n**步骤3：** 开平方根。\n$c = \\sqrt{169} = 13$。\n\n**答案：** $13$ 厘米。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-trig-angle",
        "question": "In a right-angled triangle, the opposite side is $3$ cm and the adjacent side is $4$ cm. Find the angle $\\theta$.",
        "question_zh": "在一个直角三角形中，对边为 $3$ 厘米，邻边为 $4$ 厘米。求角度 $\\theta$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Choose the correct ratio. Opposite and Adjacent involves $\\tan$.\n$\\tan(\\theta) = \\frac{3}{4} = 0.75$\n\n**Step 2:** Use the inverse function.\n$\\theta = \\tan^{-1}(0.75)$\n\n**Step 3:** Calculate (using a calculator).\n$\\theta \\approx 36.9^\\circ$.\n\n**Answer:** $36.9^\\circ$ (1 d.p.).",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 选择正确的比例。对边和邻边涉及 $\\tan$。\n$\\tan(\\theta) = \\frac{3}{4} = 0.75$\n\n**步骤2：** 使用反函数。\n$\\theta = \\tan^{-1}(0.75)$\n\n**步骤3：** 计算（使用计算器）。\n$\\theta \\approx 36.9^\\circ$。\n\n**答案：** $36.9^\\circ$（保留一位小数）。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/1H/Jan/2021"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
