  {
    "id": "kp-4.8-02",
    "section": "4.8",
    "order": 2,
    "title": "Sine and Cosine Rules",
    "title_zh": "正弦定理与余弦定理",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "For non-right-angled triangles, we use the Sine Rule and the Cosine Rule.\n\n**Sine Rule** is used when we have 'opposite pairs' of sides and angles: $\\frac{a}{\\sin A} = \\frac{b}{\\sin B} = \\frac{c}{\\sin C}$. Use it when you know two angles and one side, or two sides and a non-included angle.\n\n**Cosine Rule** is used for 'SAS' (Side-Angle-Side) or 'SSS' (Side-Side-Side) situations:\n$a^2 = b^2 + c^2 - 2bc \\cos A$\nTo find an angle: $\\cos A = \\frac{b^2 + c^2 - a^2}{2bc}$.\n\n**Area of a triangle** can be calculated using $\\frac{1}{2}ab \\sin C$.",
      "zh": "对于非直角三角形，我们使用正弦定理和余弦定理。\n\n**正弦定理**用于已知边角“对应对”的情况：$\\frac{a}{\\sin A} = \\frac{b}{\\sin B} = \\frac{c}{\\sin C}$。当已知两个角和一条边，或已知两条边和其中一边的对角时使用。\n\n**余弦定理**用于“SAS”（边角边）或“SSS”（边边边）的情况：\n$a^2 = b^2 + c^2 - 2bc \\cos A$\n求角度公式：$\\cos A = \\frac{b^2 + c^2 - a^2}{2bc}$。\n\n**三角形的面积**可以使用 $\\frac{1}{2}ab \\sin C$ 来计算。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-sine-rule",
        "label": "Calculate a side using the Sine Rule",
        "label_zh": "利用正弦定理计算边长",
        "description": "Identify an opposite pair and solve the proportion.",
        "description_zh": "识别对应边角对并解比例。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-sine-rule",
        "question": "In triangle $ABC$, $A = 40^\\circ, B = 60^\\circ$ and side $a = 10$ cm. Find side $b$.",
        "question_zh": "在三角形 $ABC$ 中，$A = 40^\\circ, B = 60^\\circ$，边 $a = 10$ 厘米。求边 $b$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Use the Sine Rule: $\\frac{a}{\\sin A} = \\frac{b}{\\sin B}$.\n$\\frac{10}{\\sin 40^\\circ} = \\frac{b}{\\sin 60^\\circ}$\n\n**Step 2:** Rearrange to solve for $b$.\n$b = \\frac{10 \\times \\sin 60^\\circ}{\\sin 40^\\circ}$\n\n**Step 3:** Calculate.\n$b \\approx \\frac{10 \\times 0.866}{0.643} \\approx 13.5$ cm.\n\n**Answer:** $13.5$ cm (3 s.f.).",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 使用正弦定理：$\\frac{a}{\\sin A} = \\frac{b}{\\sin B}$。\n$\\frac{10}{\\sin 40^\\circ} = \\frac{b}{\\sin 60^\\circ}$\n\n**步骤2：** 变形求 $b$。\n$b = \\frac{10 \\times \\sin 60^\\circ}{\\sin 40^\\circ}$\n\n**步骤3：** 计算。\n$b \\approx \\frac{10 \\times 0.866}{0.643} \\approx 13.5$ 厘米。\n\n**答案：** $13.5$ 厘米（保留 3 位有效数字）。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/2H/May/2019"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-cosine-rule",
        "question": "In triangle $XYZ$, $XY = 7$ cm, $XZ = 10$ cm and angle $X = 80^\\circ$. Calculate the length of $YZ$.",
        "question_zh": "在三角形 $XYZ$ 中，$XY = 7$ 厘米，$XZ = 10$ 厘米，角 $X = 80^\\circ$。计算 $YZ$ 的长度。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** This is SAS, so use the Cosine Rule: $a^2 = b^2 + c^2 - 2bc \\cos A$.\n$YZ^2 = 7^2 + 10^2 - 2(7)(10)\\cos 80^\\circ$\n\n**Step 2:** Simplify.\n$YZ^2 = 49 + 100 - 140 \\times 0.1736$\n$YZ^2 = 149 - 24.3 = 124.7$\n\n**Step 3:** Square root.\n$YZ = \\sqrt{124.7} \\approx 11.2$.\n\n**Answer:** $11.2$ cm.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 这是 SAS 情况，使用余弦定理：$a^2 = b^2 + c^2 - 2bc \\cos A$。\n$YZ^2 = 7^2 + 10^2 - 2(7)(10)\\cos 80^\\circ$\n\n**步骤2：** 化简。\n$YZ^2 = 49 + 100 - 140 \\times 0.1736$\n$YZ^2 = 149 - 24.3 = 124.7$\n\n**步骤3：** 开平方根。\n$YZ = \\sqrt{124.7} \\approx 11.2$。\n\n**答案：** $11.2$ 厘米。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/1H/Jan/2020"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
      {
        "q": "When do you use the Cosine Rule to find a side?",
        "q_zh": "什么时候使用余弦定理来求边长？",
        "o": [
          "When you have two angles and a side",
          "When you have three angles",
          "When you have two sides and the included angle (SAS)",
          "When you have one side and one angle"
        ],
        "a": 2,
        "e": "The Cosine Rule is required for SAS (Side-Angle-Side) or SSS (Side-Side-Side) cases.",
        "e_zh": "余弦定理适用于 SAS（边角边）或 SSS（边边边）的情况。"
      },
      {
        "q": "What is the formula for the area of a triangle using trig?",
        "q_zh": "使用三角函数计算三角形面积的公式是什么？",
        "o": [
