  {
    "id": "kp-4.9-01",
    "section": "4.9",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Arc Length and Sector Area",
    "title_zh": "弧长与扇形面积",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "A sector is a portion of a circle defined by two radii and an arc.\n\n**Arc length** is a fraction of the circumference: $L = \\frac{\\theta}{360} \\times 2\\pi r$.\n\n**Sector area** is a fraction of the circle area: $A = \\frac{\\theta}{360} \\times \\pi r^2$.\n\nHere, $\\theta$ is the angle at the center in degrees, and $r$ is the radius.",
      "zh": "扇形是由两条半径和一段弧围成的圆的一部分。\n\n**弧长**是圆周的一部分：$L = \\frac{\\theta}{360} \\times 2\\pi r$。\n\n**扇形面积**是圆面积的一部分：$A = \\frac{\\theta}{360} \\times \\pi r^2$。\n\n其中，$\\theta$ 是以度为单位的圆心角，$r$ 是半径。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-sector-calc",
        "label": "Calculate area or perimeter of a sector",
        "label_zh": "计算扇形的面积或周长",
        "description": "Remember to add the two radii if asked for the perimeter of the sector.",
        "description_zh": "如果要求扇形的周长，请记得加上两条半径。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-sector-calc",
        "question": "A sector has radius $6$ cm and angle $60^\\circ$. Calculate its area in terms of $\\pi$.",
        "question_zh": "一个扇形的半径为 $6$ 厘米，圆心角为 $60^\\circ$。用 $\\pi$ 表示其面积。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Use the sector area formula.\nArea $= \\frac{60}{360} \\times \\pi \\times 6^2$\n\n**Step 2:** Simplify the fraction and square.\nArea $= \\frac{1}{6} \\times \\pi \\times 36$\n\n**Step 3:** Calculate the final value.\nArea $= 6\\pi$.\n\n**Answer:** $6\\pi$ cm$^2$.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 使用扇形面积公式。\n面积 $= \\frac{60}{360} \\times \\pi \\times 6^2$\n\n**步骤2：** 化简分数并计算平方。\n面积 $= \\frac{1}{6} \\times \\pi \\times 36$\n\n**步骤3：** 计算最终值。\n面积 $= 6\\pi$。\n\n**答案：** $6\\pi$ cm$^2$。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-sector-calc",
        "question": "Calculate the perimeter of a sector with radius $10$ cm and center angle $72^\\circ$. Give your answer to 3 s.f.",
        "question_zh": "计算一个半径为 $10$ 厘米、圆心角为 $72^\\circ$ 的扇形的周长。保留 3 位有效数字。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Calculate the arc length.\nArc $= \\frac{72}{360} \\times 2 \\times \\pi \\times 10 = \\frac{1}{5} \\times 20\\pi = 4\\pi \\approx 12.57$ cm.\n\n**Step 2:** Add the two radii to the arc length for perimeter.\nPerimeter $= 12.57 + 10 + 10 = 32.57$ cm.\n\n**Answer:** $32.6$ cm (3 s.f.).",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 计算弧长。\n弧长 $= \\frac{72}{360} \\times 2 \\times \\pi \\times 10 = \\frac{1}{5} \\times 20\\pi = 4\\pi \\approx 12.57$ 厘米。\n\n**步骤2：** 将两条半径加到弧长上得到周长。\n周长 $= 12.57 + 10 + 10 = 32.57$ 厘米。\n\n**答案：** $32.6$ 厘米（保留 3 位有效数字）。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/1H/Jan/2021"
      }
    ],
    "testYourself": [
