  {
    "id": "kp-4.10-01",
    "section": "4.10",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "3D Shapes: Volume and Surface Area",
    "title_zh": "3D 图形：体积与表面积",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "Volume measures the space inside a 3D object, while surface area measures the total area of all its faces.\n\n**Prisms** (including cylinders) have Volume $= \\text{Area of cross-section} \\times \\text{length}$.\n\n**Pyramids and Cones** have Volume $= \\frac{1}{3} \\times \\text{Base Area} \\times \\text{Vertical Height}$.\n\n**Spheres** have Volume $= \\frac{4}{3}\\pi r^3$ and Surface Area $= 4\\pi r^2$. These formulas are often provided in the exam formula sheet.",
      "zh": "体积测量 3D 物体内部的空间，而表面积测量其所有面的总面积。\n\n**柱体**（包括圆柱体）的体积 $= \\text{横截面积} \\times \\text{长度}$。\n\n**锥体与圆锥体**的体积 $= \\frac{1}{3} \\times \\text{底面积} \\times \\text{垂直高度}$。\n\n**球体**的体积 $= \\frac{4}{3}\\pi r^3$，表面积 $= 4\\pi r^2$。这些公式通常在考试公式表中提供。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-compound-volume",
        "label": "Calculate volume of a compound 3D shape",
        "label_zh": "计算组合 3D 图形的体积",
        "description": "Find the volume of a shape made of two or more parts, like a hemisphere on top of a cylinder.",
        "description_zh": "求由两个或多个部分组成的图形的体积，例如圆柱体顶部的半球。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-compound-volume",
        "question": "A cone has a base radius of $5$ cm and a vertical height of $12$ cm. Calculate its volume.",
        "question_zh": "一个圆锥的底面半径为 $5$ 厘米，垂直高度为 $12$ 厘米。计算它的体积。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Use the formula $V = \\frac{1}{3} \\pi r^2 h$.\n$V = \\frac{1}{3} \\times \\pi \\times 5^2 \\times 12$\n\n**Step 2:** Simplify.\n$V = \\frac{1}{3} \\times \\pi \\times 25 \\times 12 = 4 \\times 25\\pi = 100\\pi$\n\n**Step 3:** Calculate decimal value if needed.\n$V \\approx 314$ cm$^3$.\n\n**Answer:** $100\\pi$ cm$^3$ or $314$ cm$^3$.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 使用公式 $V = \\frac{1}{3} \\pi r^2 h$。\n$V = \\frac{1}{3} \\times \\pi \\times 5^2 \\times 12$\n\n**步骤2：** 化简。\n$V = \\frac{1}{3} \\times \\pi \\times 25 \\times 12 = 4 \\times 25\\pi = 100\\pi$\n\n**步骤3：** 如果需要，计算小数。 \n$V \\approx 314$ cm$^3$。\n\n**答案：** $100\\pi$ cm$^3$ 或 $314$ cm$^3$。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1/1H/May/2022"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-sphere-area",
        "question": "A sphere has a diameter of $10$ cm. Calculate its surface area in terms of $\\pi$.",
        "question_zh": "一个球体的直径为 $10$ 厘米。用 $\\pi$ 表示其表面积。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Find the radius. $r = 10 / 2 = 5$ cm.\n\n**Step 2:** Use the formula $SA = 4\\pi r^2$.\n$SA = 4 \\times \\pi \\times 5^2 = 4 \\times 25\\pi = 100\\pi$.\n\n**Answer:** $100\\pi$ cm$^2$.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 求半径。$r = 10 / 2 = 5$ 厘米。\n\n**步骤2：** 使用公式 $SA = 4\\pi r^2$。\n$SA = 4 \\times \\pi \\times 5^2 = 4 \\times 25\\pi = 100\\pi$。\n\n**答案：** $100\\pi$ cm$^2$。",
        "source": "Adapted from 4MA1"
      }
